<span id="freeTextContainer7518700669962872413">I really was just being generous here with the three stars because I really had to drag myself through this book. It wasn&apos;t bad but it wasn&apos;t good either. The writing was mediocre and I couldn&apos;t bring myself to like any of the characters. I literally figured out the plot line in the beginning and the view point changes were annoying and unnecessary. I know it&apos;s a genre books but it was just so derivative of every other mystery book I&apos;ve read, there was nothing original or good about it. You can&apos;</span>
  <span id="freeText7518700669962872413" style="display:none">I really was just being generous here with the three stars because I really had to drag myself through this book. It wasn't bad but it wasn't good either. The writing was mediocre and I couldn't bring myself to like any of the characters. I literally figured out the plot line in the beginning and the view point changes were annoying and unnecessary. I know it's a genre books but it was just so derivative of every other mystery book I've read, there was nothing original or good about it. You can't be a mediocre writer with boring cliched characters and a predictable plot line like come on man give me something.</span>
